## Project Structure

```text
packages/
  shared-types/   # Core interfaces and validators
  bot-adapters/   # Telegram/Discord adapter implementations
  gateway/        # HTTP gateway server
  cli/            # CLI commands (onboard, pairing, gateway, agent)
  ai-agent/       # AI provider factory, conversation store, message processor, tools
tests/
  unit/           # Unit tests mirror packages/ structure
  integration/    # End-to-end flow tests
  contract/       # API surface contract tests
  __mocks__/      # Shared test mocks
docs/             # User-facing documentation (getting-started, CLI ref, feature guides)
specs/            # Feature specifications and plans
```

## Commands

```bash
pnpm test                # Run all tests
pnpm test:coverage       # Run tests with coverage thresholds
pnpm lint                # Run oxlint
pnpm format:check        # Check Prettier formatting
pnpm format              # Auto-fix formatting
pnpm build               # Build all packages
```

## Code Style

TypeScript 5.x strict mode. No `any`. No comments. Small functions. Dependency injection everywhere.

